# Public environment variables consumed by the Vite client build.
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (gitignored) and fill in real values.

# Brandfetch Logo Link client ID. Used by the /clients page to render
# brand-supplied logos for clients that don't yet have a logo file on disk
# under public/clients/.
#
# How to get one:
#   1. Sign up at https://developers.brandfetch.com (free)
#   2. Create a project, copy the Client ID
#   3. Paste below
#
# Free tier: 25,000 logo requests / month. No credit card required.
# When unset, the /clients page silently falls back to initials monograms
# for clients without a local logo file — no error, no broken images.
VITE_BRANDFETCH_CLIENT_ID=
